Pp3cloud ( http://www.pp3.cloud/tag/brazil ) is an interactive database/web site dedicated to tracking POCs (possible political prisoners) in Brazil.\
\
Anyone in the world can register on http://www.pp3.cloud/tag/brazil and report any number of victims of unjust imprisonment, upload photographs, write biographical data, attach newslinks and blogs, all of which are entered into the database and appear immediately on the website. No other website has these capabilities.\
